"= Display ON.<br>MAIN-: ACC MAIN on = Display OFF<br>OP-: OP enabled = "
"Display OFF."
msgstr ""
"标准：原厂行为。<br>MAIN+：ACC MAIN 开启 = 屏幕开启。<br>OP+：OP 启用 = 屏幕"
"开启。<br>MAIN-：ACC MAIN 开启 = 屏幕关闭。<br>OP-：OP 启用 = 屏幕关闭。"

#: dragonpilot/settings/min-feat.dev.alert-mode.py:9
